{"tw": {"3063520": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "LISC - Season 1", "steam_appid": 3063520, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想像一下，你終於搬進了夢寐以求的新居，而這一切都要感謝那位一直給予你靈感與支持的她——還能有什麼意外？然而，世事難料，她突然遭到不公的指控，讓你才開始的嶄新生活陷入動盪。此刻，全靠你站出來為她辯護，同時還得讓與你朝夕相處的五位重要女性，在同一屋簷下依然能安心快樂。聽起來似乎不算複雜？可別忘了，這五個人性格各異，你不僅要想辦法同時應對，還得抽絲剝繭地尋找真相，守護你才剛奠定的未來。勇氣、機智和耐心，缺一不可！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入這段既溫暖又輕鬆的旅程，去探索你究竟能為心中珍視的人做到何種地步。命運已向你發出邀請，你的決定，將為彼此帶來全新的開始！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063520/extras/2530dcbaa6176048f07e8f4422950d0c.poster.avif?t=1759770620\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063520/extras/2530dcbaa6176048f07e8f4422950d0c.webm?t=1759770620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063520/extras/2530dcbaa6176048f07e8f4422950d0c.mp4?t=1759770620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超過 10,000 張精美靜態畫面</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >300 段火熱動畫場景</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 ~ 10 小時的遊戲流程</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多樣刺激情節，與你心動的她們親密互動</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同身材、風格與魅力的迷人角色，總有你喜歡的類型</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >數百種音效，讓體驗更沉浸、更生動</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>與心目中的理想之人來一場浪漫約會</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063520/extras/74b891ce2755841e0e5686506e89db32.avif?t=1759770620\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic